<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.10">
<l>naṉṉīr vayalpuṭaicūḻ naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampiyai</l>
<l>kaṉīra mālvaraittōḷ kalikaṉṟi maṅkaiyarkōṉ</l>
<l>coṉīra colmālai colvārkaḷ cūḻvicumpil</l>
<l>naṉīrmai yālmakiḻntu neṭunkālam vāḻvārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who say this garland of words whose essence is recitation of the king</l>
<l rend="indent">of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>Kalikaṉṟi with shoulders [like] a huge mountain whose essence is stone,</l>
<l>About the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where good,</l>
<l rend="indent">wet fields circle on [all] sides,</l>
<l>Rejoicing with a good temperament, they will live for a long time</l>
<l rend="indent">in the encircling heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
